<P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#CCCCCC><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukorvusjunode.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Korvus Junode</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>3/25/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>2:34:07 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: My position on isle seven in Sky</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">   I can't find the proper quote but I think Ralph Koster of all people got it right. Give a person a chance to manipulate the system in an mmorpg and they will take every advantage of it they can. It's suprising this hasn't already happened.<br>
<br>
   I'm saddened to see the abuse of what was at the time a generous act.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#F5F5DC><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uthanatosia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Thanatosia</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>3/25/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>11:22:18 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://www.eternusastralis.com/site/logo/ea60x60.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Whats wrong with ppl???</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">No offense, but the way I'm seeing it is some ppl are going out of their way spending their time and effort to altruistically help other Magicians throught a difficult part of their epic quest and now we are bitching about them doing this good deed because they are letting ppl do things easier then what we want them to have to do.<br>
<br>
Maybe we have some small reason to post negatively about the Magicians accepting this offer, but I realy dont think so. And for the ppl who are spending their time and resources to help others for no gain to themselves - its just wrong to flame them.<br>
<br>
This is the kind of thing that makes Prexus a community that I want to be in. Its a random act of kindness. Dont discourage it please. They are rare enough as it is.<br>
<br>
Now, if they are not doing this altruistically and charging for the right to get crowns (more then coffin/airstone expenses at least) at a profit; then I agree, this is abhorant. But if they are doing it just out of sheer goodwill, screw it, let them do it, and leave them alone plz. </font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#CCCCCC><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utalulabloodroses.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Talula Bloodroses</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://cwm.ragesofsanity.com/s/net4/viking.gif width=25 height = 25 BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>3/26/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>12:40:07 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://www.public.iastate.edu/~garden/music/tori/thumb/t_orgasmic.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Whats wrong with ppl???</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">/agree Thana</font><P><img src=http://surfree.homestead.com/Talula/files/Talulasig3.JPG>
<BR>
<i>Sometimes you're nothing but meat...</i><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#F5F5DC><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ubremmin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bremmin</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>3/26/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>1:47:43 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://www.eternusastralis.com/site/logo/ea60x60.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Whats wrong with ppl???</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">You know, you could come to me with every magician who is a friend of mine, and I wouldn't be able to tell them to their face that I didn't want them to get their epic. In fact, you could probably set any mage in front of me, and I wouldn't be able to say that. <br>
<br>
In my opinion fighting to Isle Seven for every mage who needs a crown would altruism. <br>
<br>
This is not Altruism.<br>
<br>
What is happening now is that a precedence is being set that says this:<br>
<br>
We are willing to exploit whatever we can.<br>
<br>
We are willing to demean any accomplishment we can.<br>
<br>
For me, if this happens, where people who I have never even heard of, where people who weren't even anywhere near completing their epic at the time, start getting crowns, I don't know what I'll do.<br>
<br>
I don't think I could play this game knowing my guild was responsible for a system that turned what used to be my favorite zone in the game into nothing more than a big joke. <br>
<br>
As far as I'm concerned, any mage who isn't worth his salt shouldn't be getting a crown. Unfortunately, I'm not able to make that determination for every mage on the server, I don't know all of them. Unfortunately, we've also removed the only reliable mechanism for determining who is. <br>
</font><P>--Bremmin Ironsoul<BR>
